<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="R" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Rocky" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Rocky,</orth> consisting of rocks: <cit><quote>r. shore,</quote> <bibl n="shak. r2 2.1.62" default="NO" valid="yes">R2 II, 1, 62</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>as firm as r. mountains,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 2h4 4.1.188" default="NO" valid="yes">H4B IV, 1, 188</bibl></cit>. Metaphorically, == hard, unfeeling: <cit><quote>thy r. and wreck-threatening heart,</quote> <bibl n="shak. luc 590" default="NO" valid="yes">Lucr. 590</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. lc 291" default="NO" valid="yes">Compl. 291</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r3 4.4.234" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 IV, 4, 234</bibl>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>